{"type":"data","nodes":[{"type":"data","data":[{"debug":1},true],"uses":{}},{"type":"data","data":[{"zotero":1,"inscriptions":7,"isBulletin":572},{"title":2,"author":3,"date":4,"citation":5,"uri":6},"Sicile","Orsi","1896","\u003Cspan>Paolo Orsi, « Sicile », \u003Ci>Bulletin de Correspondance Hellénique\u003C/i> 20 (1896): 399‑400\u003C/span>","https://www.zotero.org/groups/isicily/items/FWX5CWBN",[8,118,174,263,330,396],{"file":9,"uri":9,"title":10,"status":11,"editionAuthor":13,"type":14,"objectType":18,"material":22,"condition":28,"layoutDesc":29,"handNote":36,"date":52,"places":57,"geo":67,"country":62,"provenance":59,"provenanceGeo":71,"region":74,"settlement":75,"repository":76,"idno":80,"textLang":83,"tmNumber":28,"letterHeights":87,"publications":91,"zotero":95,"keywords":99,"html":110,"bibl":111,"bulletinDateSort":117,"citedRangeSort":112,"languageSort":84,"materialSort":23,"typeSort":15},"ISic001869","Funerary inscription for Artemo",{"_":12},"edited",null,{"_":15,"ana":16,"ref":17},"funerary","#function.funerary","http://www.eagle-network.eu/voc/typeins/lod/92.html",{"_":19,"ana":20,"ref":21},"block","#object.block","http://www.eagle-network.eu/voc/objtyp/lod/189.html",{"_":23,"type":24,"subtype":25,"ref":27},"limestone","inorganic.stone",[26],"unverified","http://www.eagle-network.eu/voc/material/lod/66.html","",{"layout":30},{"p":31,"rs":32,"damage":28},"Three lines of Greek letters, seemingly not centered / regularly laid out.",{"_":33,"ana":34,"ref":35},"chiselled","#execution.chiselled","http://www.eagle-network.eu/voc/writing/lod/1",{"lettering":37,"dimensions":38},"Described by Orsi (1896) as 'scritto a pessimi caratteri', and (1899) as 'lettere cattive, rustiche cosi che a tutta prima sembrano archaiche, e molto sconservate... L'iscrizione negligentemente redatta e scolpita è funebre di tarda età'. Pace states 'lettere del III sec. av. Cr.', but given the presence of lunate epsilon and Orsi's comments, a later date seems much more likely.",[39,48],